headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Double GTA$ & RP in Drop Zone, Power Play & Kill Quota plus Discounts on Property, Vehicles and More
content:
Satisfy your paratrooper fantasy in Drop Zone or let your inner Beast run amok in Power Play, both of which are delivering Double GTA$ and RP now through December 7, along with ongoing Double GTA$ & RP in Kill Quota.

And bolster the style and security of your operation with 50% off Executive Offices and discounts on various vehicles and weaponry this week.

Check out the Rockstar Newswire for all the details.
